lead_paragraph: Forward Nacer Chadli has joined West Bromwich Albion from Premier League rivals Tottenham Hotspur on a four-year contract, both clubs announced on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Spurs Forward Chadli Joins West Brom on Four-Year Deal
